{"tid":44790,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得哲學應該成為必修科既入一入黎","createTime":"2016-12-18T14:07:20.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T14:12:51.000Z","uid":12185,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a0ae29b3beac2ef7384004b5b2252ad9b5b88baf","tid":44790,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:07:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/shared?ci=VjVb0WKhuRo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fshared%3Fci%3DVjVb0WKhuRo&d=mRKhycZ0hvTWpSKDX%2FBG%2F0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=6b351695\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/shared?ci=VjVb0WKhuRo</a><br />\n<br />\n呢條片講得真係好好<br />\n就算你對哲學有好多認識，<br />\n冇歷史、冇文化、冇藝術、冇科學既認識，<br />\n就好似你有一部高級咖啡機，<br />\n但係得啲百佳咖啡豆咁<br />\n有思辯技巧但冇內容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n與其必修哲學<br />\n不如必修中西史<br />\n就算你識存在主義，<br />\n但你唔知存在主義同一二冷戰既關係<br />\n識正義論，但唔知福利社會既出現<br />\n只係將本身已經唔貼地既野再抽離佢個context<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44b7462d2d1bffb4c9e0084b3f7164d0c9b15723","tid":44790,"uid":3926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:11:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f98a8af92a388cea6e00d7ce3e6ef12d2b083fe1","tid":44790,"uid":34834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:12:49.000Z","msg":"永遠文史哲根本就唔可以分家"},{"pid":"c01b5a5077b2bab2172afa7be67b884fb8eeee42","tid":44790,"uid":34834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:13:30.000Z","msg":"利申有讀英國文學但好少讀歷史"},{"pid":"32341e05f24f46a5f7faecd529b46ce58d7bb6db","tid":44790,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:17:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>永遠文史哲根本就唔可以分家</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講真你讀左文史之後<br />\n(科學都得，理科仔唔好屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n就算唔刻意去鑽研，<br />\n最尾都一定會引導到去哲學層面，<br />\n只係皮毛同深入既分別"},{"pid":"19e6b2cb3aba672f675f1271d66c263266742e47","tid":44790,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:20:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利申有讀英國文學但好少讀歷史</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讀文學好難唔識歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1fd6c217461cc0a090edb55b00f73ae005dd03","tid":44790,"uid":56524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:26:42.000Z","msg":"好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"917835fcfa5d0f2a35ef024a77073c377af90fa8","tid":44790,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:30:40.000Z","msg":"正解 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"086e5ed18bef5ff6fac4e1882ed24e0d8d77c486","tid":44790,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:33:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc2283d262b09df892a0a047933afce739d176d1","tid":44790,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:35:53.000Z","msg":"理科撚表示將文史哲分家會難讀到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b95b55400de83d04c0cd06ce7f8fe2900da4de0a","tid":44790,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:47:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>理科撚表示將文史哲分家會難讀到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得史可以獨立咁讀，<br />\n但係淨係讀哲/文真係濕滯啲，<br />\n好多野會唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"250237449ec7c7e00d7ad774285ec3de327963ba","tid":44790,"uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:22:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>利申有讀英國文學但好少讀歷史</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讀文學好難唔識歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真，至少讀中國文學一定識中史"},{"pid":"fe7d7566645f5bb1b4bbedf3307047c54142f156","tid":44790,"uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:22:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>理科撚表示將文史哲分家會難讀到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得史可以獨立咁讀，<br />\n但係淨係讀哲/文真係濕滯啲，<br />\n好多野會唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n單係讀文學，唔讀作者背景，已經好難理解篇文，除非你堅持結構主義"},{"pid":"613fe86ea32842aa92aa07b51e52cf836e383e3d","tid":44790,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T19:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6231db6451bcc8180b11584015e4aa70b50e6ff9","tid":44790,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T21:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a1ccc998182a9a910847d8ad523a138d7f5f65f","tid":44790,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T21:53:04.000Z","msg":"咁點解唔整一科人文科？<br />\n教文史哲入門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1fd07b577d0538f9ca215d090711a1758a4adc6","tid":44790,"uid":54883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T22:01:32.000Z","msg":"必修但係你覺得中學班老師有咁既學術水平可以教到?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n規定八大必修就差唔多，不果以我所知，好似都唔少大學要必修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />起碼我個間要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14ce90e2abd7aa970ca1a0eef793c854c5a7f9c1","tid":44790,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:37:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁點解唔整一科人文科？<br />\n教文史哲入門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4594b560c30b809b743b9cd98d35ff82355f3ec5","tid":44790,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:38:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>必修但係你覺得中學班老師有咁既學術水平可以教到?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n規定八大必修就差唔多，不果以我所知，好似都唔少大學要必修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />起碼我個間要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHKU唔使<br />\n應該必修文史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f9b44f8361ae57876d5e059f6fa3cc7a7dab6b","tid":44790,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T00:33:13.000Z","msg":"存在主義同一二冷戰既關係<br />\n識正義論，但唔知福利社會既出現<br />\n<br />\n一個有責任心既哲學老師係會講埋呢d"},{"pid":"750049e3e272662113424489ab15a5fd178e9141","tid":44790,"uid":23701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T09:08:42.000Z","msg":"要睇，哲學成為必修科佢教既模式係點。<br />\n博柯式既哲學？以哲學問題做中心，哲學史式哲學？純教分析哲學？<br />\n我覺得係最後個一個option 先會有成為思考機器既問題。<br />\n中哲我覺得就，文哲係分家既。不過戰國之後得番儒同佛既哲學係可憐既<br />\n其實中西史做左必修課，都會有一堆背誦機器既問題。"},{"pid":"3ce84445396df3dfd2b15ae4fb41e82bfa39bef5","tid":44790,"uid":60166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:45:12.000Z","msg":"讀得哲學多就自然想睇埋歷史，根本冇得分家"},{"pid":"2823f4f3df084e915f061cd4b880d98abb4a569b","tid":44790,"uid":34834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T14:12:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>&lt;blockquote&gt;利申有讀英國文學但好少讀歷史</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讀文學好難唔識歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n<br />\n認真，至少讀中國文學一定識中史</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會識既但唔多，大概講下個氛圍咁，者係讀victorian lit就係咁二講下工業革命同個輪興既utilitarianism <br />\n者係你問我邊個係政治上做左d咩，對個社會個影響有咩就難答d<br />\n好多時點到即止，夠解倒小說背景就停"}]}